name: Albedo (Overlord)
description:
It is a character LoRA of Albedo from Overlord. It was trained on AbyssOrangeMix2_hard model.

For better results add

  • with v1.0: add "white horns"

  • with v1.1 (EXPERIMENTAL): "white horns, black wings, black hair, white dress"
